@startuml School Management System

actor Student
boundary "School System" as SchoolSystem
actor Admin
entity EducationalInformation
entity FinancialInformation

note over Student, SchoolSystem
Student applies for enrollment
end note

Student -> SchoolSystem: Apply for Enrollment

SchoolSystem -> Admin: Receive Enrollment Application

Admin -> EducationalInformation: Verify Eligibility

EducationalInformation -> Admin: Eligibility Verified

Admin -> FinancialInformation: Process Fees

FinancialInformation --> Admin: Fees Processed

Admin -> SchoolSystem: Confirm Enrollment

SchoolSystem --> Admin: Enrollment Confirmed

Admin --> Student: Enrollment Confirmation

note over Student, SchoolSystem
Student applies for enrollment
end note

actor Student
boundary SchoolSystem
entity EducationalInformation

Student -> SchoolSystem: View Educational Information
activate SchoolSystem
SchoolSystem -> EducationalInformation: Retrieve Educational Information
activate EducationalInformation
EducationalInformation --> SchoolSystem: Educational Information
deactivate EducationalInformation
SchoolSystem --> Student: Display Educational Information
deactivate SchoolSystem

@enduml